OL,3,CYvette Cooper continues Saudi visit as
OL,4,CIran threatens to block key oil route
OL,6,FThe Foreign Secretary will continue
OL,7,Fher visit to Saudi Arabia on Friday
OL,8,Famid continued concern about Iranian
OL,9,Fthreats to the Strait of Hormuz.
OL,11,FShe arrived in the country on Thursday
OL,12,Fin a show of solidarity with Gulf
OL,13,Fstates hit by Iran's retaliation to
OL,14,Fongoing joint US-Israeli strikes.
OL,16,FSince then, Iran's new supreme leader
OL,17,Fhas threatened to continue attacks on
OL,18,Fthe country's neighbours until they
OL,19,F"expel the Americans" as he vowed to
OL,20,Favenge "martyrs" killed in the
OL,21,Fconflict.
OL,26,@{D@AOU{D@UO]|D@HOU|D@PO]
