OL,3,CYvette Cooper continues Saudi visit as
OL,4,CIran threatens to block key oil route
OL,6,FIn a written statement read out on
OL,7,FIranian television by a news anchor,
OL,8,FAyatollah Mojtaba Khamenei also
OL,9,Fthreatened to continue blocking the
OL,10,FStrait of Hormuz, a vital shipping
OL,11,Flane for oil from the Gulf.
OL,13,FThe effective blockade of the strait
OL,14,Fhas seen oil prices spike, touching
OL,15,F100 dollars per barrel again on
OL,16,FThursday and threatening higher
OL,17,Finflation in the UK and across the
OL,18,Fworld.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773370999
OL,3,CYvette Cooper continues Saudi visit as
OL,4,CIran threatens to block key oil route
OL,6,FAgainst that background, Prime
OL,7,FMinister Sir Keir Starmer said he
OL,8,Fwould work to "de-escalate the
OL,9,Fsituation" and was co-ordinating with
OL,10,Fother world leaders on the supply of
OL,11,Foil.
OL,13,FPart of that effort saw Ms Cooper meet
OL,14,Fa range of Saudi ministers on
OL,15,FThursday, including the energy
OL,16,Fminister and foreign minister.
OL,26,@pD@OOUqD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
