OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773370999
OL,3,CYvette Cooper continues Saudi visit as
OL,4,CIran threatens to block key oil route
OL,6,FAnd she addressed a special meeting of
OL,7,Fthe Gulf Co-operation Council's (GCC)
OL,8,Fforeign ministers on regional
OL,9,Fstability and Mr Khamenei's threats to
OL,10,Fthe Strait of Hormuz.
OL,12,FGCC secretary-general Jasem Al-Budaiwi
OL,13,Fthanked Ms Cooper for the UK's
OL,14,Fmilitary and "moral support".
OL,16,FThe UK continues to carry out
OL,17,Fdefensive operations in the region,
OL,18,Fincluding RAF jets flying sorties over
OL,19,FJordan, Qatar and the UAE to protect
OL,20,Fagainst drone attacks.
OL,26,@vD@NOUvD@\O]
