OL,3,CYvette Cooper continues Saudi visit as
OL,4,CIran threatens to block key oil route
OL,6,FBritish troops came under attack at a
OL,7,Fmilitary base in Erbil, Iraq, on
OL,8,FWednesday night, defence chiefs have
OL,9,Fsaid.
OL,11,FDefence Secretary John Healey was
OL,12,Fbriefed on the latest updates on
OL,13,FBritish action in the conflict in the
OL,14,FMiddle East during a visit to the
OL,15,FNorthwood military headquarters in
OL,16,FHertfordshire on Thursday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
