OL,3,CYvette Cooper continues Saudi visit as
OL,4,CIran threatens to block key oil route
OL,6,FAsked on Thursday whether the UK would
OL,7,Fbe prepared to participate in a patrol
OL,8,Fof the straits, the minister said it
OL,9,Fwas "early days" and insisted there
OL,10,Fwas an "international imperative" to
OL,11,Fresolve the situation.
OL,13,FDemining any waters would be
OL,14,F"extremely difficult," he said, adding
OL,15,Fthat he was having discussions with
OL,16,Fplanners and that there were already
OL,17,Fsome demining autonomous systems in
OL,18,Fplace in the region since before the
OL,19,Fconflict.
OL,26,@qD@EOUqD@PO]rD@HOUrD@aO]vD@AOUvD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773370999
OL,3,CYvette Cooper continues Saudi visit as
OL,4,CIran threatens to block key oil route
OL,6,F"In the end, this is likely to be most
OL,7,Fquickly sorted and the straits are
OL,8,Fmost likely to be quickly opened by a
OL,9,Fde-escalation of the conflict, by a
OL,10,Fgreater stabilisation and confidence
OL,11,Fin the region and by all those nations
OL,12,Fthat want to see the straits reopened
OL,13,Fbeing willing to work together."
OL,15,FThe Defence Secretary warned that
OL,16,FVladimir Putin's "hidden hand" was
OL,17,Fbehind some of the Iranian tactics and
OL,18,Fthat the Russian president was
OL,19,Fbenefitting from the surge in oil
OL,20,Fprices triggered by the conflict.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@`O]xD@ROUxD@^O]
