OL,3,CYvette Cooper continues Saudi visit as
OL,4,CIran threatens to block key oil route
OL,6,F"It helps him with a fresh supply of
OL,7,Ffunds for his brutal war in Ukraine,"
OL,8,Fhe said.
OL,10,FOn Friday, French President Emmanuel
OL,11,FMacron confirmed a French soldier had
OL,12,Fbeen killed in an attack targeting
OL,13,FErbil and several others had been
OL,14,Finjured.
OL,16,FIn a post on X, Mr Macron said: "To
OL,17,Fhis family, to his brothers in arms, I
OL,18,Fwant to express all the affection and
OL,19,Fsolidarity of the Nation."
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@eO]xD@aOU{D@ZO]
